<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 20px;">📅 New Timetable Published!</h2>

<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #374151;">Hello {{recipientName}},</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">
    Great news! A new timetable has been published for <strong style="color: #1f2937;">{{batchName}}</strong> 
    and is now available for viewing.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <strong style="font-size: 16px; color: #1f2937;">📋 Timetable Details:</strong>
    <table style="width: 100%; margin-top: 15px; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Batch:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{batchName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Section:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{section}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Semester:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">Semester {{semester}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Course:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{courseName}} ({{courseCode}})</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Department:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{departmentName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Academic Year:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{academicYear}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong style="color: #374151;">Published On:</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right; color: #1f2937;">{{publishedDate}} at {{publishedTime}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{timetableUrl}}" class="button">View Your Timetable</a>
</p>

<p><strong>📌 What's Next?</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Review your complete class schedule</li>
    <li>Note down your classroom assignments</li>
    <li>Check faculty assignments for each subject</li>
    <li>Mark important dates on your calendar</li>
    <li>Prepare your materials for the upcoming classes</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box">
    <strong>💡 Pro Tips:</strong>
    <ul style="margin: 5px 0;">
        <li>Download or print your timetable for offline access</li>
        <li>Set reminders for your classes</li>
        <li>Familiarize yourself with classroom locations</li>
        <li>Share the schedule with your peers</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions or notice any issues with your timetable, please contact your class coordinator immediately.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br><strong>Academic Compass Team</strong></p>
